subproject.corporate outcome: Capacities of national and local institutions enhanced to scale up proven MDG acceleration interventions and to plan, monitor, report and evaluate the MDG progress in the context of related national development priorities
subproject.description: The NHDR is a tool aimed at raising awareness on substantive issues related to Human Development by providing data and analysis on human development issues. It also serves as a major advocacy tool for influencing national and sub-national agendas towards the promotion and achievement of higher levels of human development.
subproject.title: UGA0219 Natnal Humn Dev.Rprt
